Name: Country Girl Keiko
About the game: Keiko lives in a small countryside village named Cocco. Here she attends the local agricultural university. This university is very strict, and she is asked by a professor to help get some troublesome students to stop skipping classes. However, Keiko is socially awkward, and needs to learn how to interact with others. Features: Slice of Life RPG Explore a Japanese country village Help Keiko become more self-confident
